  "short_description": "The World has flipped, everything's in chaos... but hey, you're a Fool — you're used to it. Strategically pick your Minor Arcana for each stage. Collect powerful Major Arcana as you go, each one rewriting your destiny. Your fate lies in the cards — choose wisely or stay a Fool forever!",
