  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/7adc80a5d590f32469d7a509f199c426.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tarot card themed rogue-lite action game testing your reflex.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock playable Major Arcana with unique skills and playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic rogue-lite gameplay by combining different Minor Arcana.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Extra</i> rogue-lite gameplay with stage adjustments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging levels and bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Appreciate the beautiful original Rider-Waite public domain artwork.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your mouse and control your fate to survive the Star, Moon, Sun and Judgement and flip the World back to normal!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each Major Arcana has their unique active and passive skills!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/ba668ebb74b6d50d2376c791838153d6.avif?t=1749509180\" width=656 height=440 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Utilize the Minor Arcana each with their unique readings to help you survive!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/1111c17e28ee383b7a6d2f39e50341ea.avif?t=1749509180\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras_big/1111c17e28ee383b7a6d2f39e50341ea.avif?t=1749509180 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Carefully select the Major Arcana that changes the stage difficulty!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/3324f4522059f1dfc26130ca329709d8.avif?t=1749509180\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras_big/3324f4522059f1dfc26130ca329709d8.avif?t=1749509180 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grab another mouse and a friend for local co-op and challenge your friendship!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/0daea911001158dc4c5b6b0db750ddf1.avif?t=1749509180\" width=656 height=440 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat the different stages and explore blocks with unique effects!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/2bd53b305ae7abd6b2e699a927c45b3a.avif?t=1749509180\" width=600 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/9667ac600591db4f00987addeb3732d5.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/b9ff5ceebaeaea38ccad9002ab69d1de.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/a597b62907a0ddcb04c5de717ef5c615.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/4cdaaaee6ccdb9694c6b7b465be4a5f3.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/7adc80a5d590f32469d7a509f199c426.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tarot card themed rogue-lite action game testing your reflex.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock playable Major Arcana with unique skills and playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic rogue-lite gameplay by combining different Minor Arcana.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Extra</i> rogue-lite gameplay with stage adjustments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging levels and bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Appreciate the beautiful original Rider-Waite public domain artwork.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your mouse and control your fate to survive the Star, Moon, Sun and Judgement and flip the World back to normal!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each Major Arcana has their unique active and passive skills!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/ba668ebb74b6d50d2376c791838153d6.avif?t=1749509180\" width=656 height=440 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Utilize the Minor Arcana each with their unique readings to help you survive!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/1111c17e28ee383b7a6d2f39e50341ea.avif?t=1749509180\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras_big/1111c17e28ee383b7a6d2f39e50341ea.avif?t=1749509180 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Carefully select the Major Arcana that changes the stage difficulty!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/3324f4522059f1dfc26130ca329709d8.avif?t=1749509180\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras_big/3324f4522059f1dfc26130ca329709d8.avif?t=1749509180 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grab another mouse and a friend for local co-op and challenge your friendship!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/0daea911001158dc4c5b6b0db750ddf1.avif?t=1749509180\" width=656 height=440 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat the different stages and explore blocks with unique effects!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/2bd53b305ae7abd6b2e699a927c45b3a.avif?t=1749509180\" width=600 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/9667ac600591db4f00987addeb3732d5.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/b9ff5ceebaeaea38ccad9002ab69d1de.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/a597b62907a0ddcb04c5de717ef5c615.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 height=32 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3665270/extras/4cdaaaee6ccdb9694c6b7b465be4a5f3.webp?t=1749509180\" width=32 he